org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.namenode

Interface CheckableNameNodeResource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JournalSet.JournalAndStream, NameNodeResourceChecker.CheckedVolume

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
interface CheckableNameNodeResource
    Implementers of this class represent a NN resource whose availability can be checked. A resource can be either "required" or "redundant". All required resources must be available for the NN to continue operating. The NN will continue to operate as long as *any* redundant resource is available.
